---
title: Lemony Fish & Chips with Yogurt Tartar Sauce
description: The key to great fish and chips is a good quality fillet of fish and a delicious dip. We've created our own yogurt-based tartar sauce, and are sharing our delicious blend with you! Roasted sweet potatoes add a hit of sweetness and a dose of beta-carotene, essential for good eye health!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemony-fish-chips-052a7695.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/lemony-fish-chips-98a2f736.pdf
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
